## Scope Boundary

This public SDK covers only the application-layer Möbius phase-aware retrieval interface.

This license notice does not grant rights to private RetryIX technologies, including but not limited to:

- RetryIX private runtime internals
- MemoryKernel internal scheduling
- VirtualPIM resident execution paths
- TurboQuant-compatible backend internals
- SPD / EEPROM physical memory interface designs
- Hardware-specific routing logic
- Patent-sensitive RetryIX core technology

